  "description": "Conductor V2 — configure the swarm before you fire it. Pick a topology (hierarchical / pipeline / mesh), load a preset (deep research / market bots / web3+security), set the purpose, FIRE: a fleet of Claude Code windows on Fable 5, coordinating over tmux, watched from one cockpit.",
